title: Asian Retro Food: Dishes of Yesteryear (2009) pdf
description:
In the first of its kind, Betty Saw's latest cookbook brings back the good ol' Asian favourites of yesteryear. These long forgotten recipes will not only bring back fond memories of years past, they will also acquaint the younger generation with the dishes their parents and grandparents enjoyed. 

 From vegetables to poultry and noodles to desserts, take a trip down memory lane with Betty Saw.
